<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA40">
<l>maṟittu maṭaneñcē vāyāluñ collik</l>
<l>kuṟittut toḻutoṇṭar pātaṅ - kuṟittoruvar</l>
<l>koḷḷāta tiṅkaṭ kuṟuṅkaṇṇi koṇṭārmāṭ</l>
<l>ṭuḷḷātār kūṭṭa moruvu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Change, ignorant heart, speaking with the mouth,</l>
<l>intent on the feet of the servants who worship with intent,</l>
<l>renounce the company of those who do not think</l>
<l>about him who took the moon as a short chaplet which is not taken by anyone.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
